Function Reference/the author « WordPress Codex
-----------

The author of a post can be **displayed** by using this [Template
Tag](/Template_Tags "Template Tags"). This tag must be used within [The
Loop](/The_Loop "The Loop").

To **return** to PHP rather than displaying, use
[get\_the\_author](/Template_Tags/get_the_author "Template Tags/get the author").

Usage
-----

`  <?php the_author(); ?> `

Examples
--------

### Display Author's 'Public' Name

Displays the value in the user's **Display name publicly as** field.

    <p>This post was written by <?php the_author(); ?></p>

Parameters
----------

\$post-id (integer).

